      <li>Bachelor's Degree in computer science.</li>
      <li>5+ years actively participating in software development projects mostly in systems areas.</li>
      <li>In depth knowledge of C/C++ on Unix platforms, with thorough understanding of system programming, network protocols, high performance and distributed systems.</li>
      <li>Familiarity with Windows development is a plus </li>
      <li>Experience working in a fast paced, highly technical environment </li>
